data.description: There is no other home like this available for sale at this price in North Aurora! Upon entering the front door, you will appreciate the cathedral ceilings, the flow of the layout and warmth of the neutral color palette. The location of the bedrooms is perfect for so many buyers with 2 BR/1 BA upstairs and 1 BR (currently used as an office)/1 BA on the lower level. Although the bedrooms upstairs share a bathroom, there is private access from the primary bedroom. In addition to the third bedroom on the lower level, there is a nice large family/rec room and access to the sub-basement which is partially finished. The unfinished portion houses the washer/dryer and built-in shelving units for storage! The bay in the eat-in kitchen leads out to the 2-tiered deck with sun sails for shade and a large, fenced yard! This home has been meticulously maintained, freshly painted and ready for new owners. Chesterfield Park is just a few blocks away. You are going to love it!
